channel.title: "unexpected response from server" shown in client for others but not me
channel.description:
Hey,
I'm making a server and was going to do my first beta run of all the features I currently have. When my friend tried to login, he got "unexpected reponse from server" however when I use exactly the same client as him it works fine.
There are also no errors. Any suggestions? The version is 550 and I'm using scapeemulator base. Thanks
